  <billdetail>
    <title>Te Pire a Ngati Tuwharetoa, Raukawa, me te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa mō te Awa o Waikato</title>
    <billtype>He Pire Kāwanatanga</billtype>
    <repnote>Ki tā te Komiti Whiriwhiri Take Māori i whakatakoto</repnote>
    <commentary id="DLM3191501" in.amend="false" irdnumbering="no" official="yes" bill.no="143" bill.type="government" stage="2" year="2010">
      <heading>Ngā Kōrero</heading>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Tūtohutanga</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Kua āta tirohia te Pire a Ngati Tuwharetoa, Raukawa, me te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa mō te Awa o Waikato, e te Komiti Whiriwhiri Take Māori, ā, ka tūtohu kia whakamanahia, me ngā whakatikatika kua whakaaturia.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Kupu Whakataki</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Ka whakamana te Pire a Ngati Tuwharetoa, Raukawa, me te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa mō te Awa o Waikato i ngā whakaaetanga i uru atu te Karauna me Ngāti Tūwharetoa, Raukawa, me te Awa Iwi o Te Arawa ki roto, ā, nā te pērātanga, ka whakaae te Karauna me ia iwi ki tētahi pou tarāwaho whakahaere tiaki kaupapa-tahi mō te Awa o Waikato, tae atu ki ōna rohenga wai, me ngā whakaritenga e pā ana ki tētahi whakahaere-tahi, kia ora anō ake ai te hauora me te oranga o te Awa o Waikato, mō ngā whakatipuranga o nāianei, o ngā rā hoki kei te tū mai, ā, kia tiakina hoki.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Kīnaki ai te pire nei i ngā whakaritenga i whakaaetia i waenganui i te Karauna me Waikato-Tainui, i tētahi whakaaetanga whakataunga i hainatia i te 17 o Hakihea i te tau 2009, waihoki, kua tuhia ngā wāhanga (mō Waikato-Tainui), ki roto i te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato) o te tau 2010.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Ngā whakaaetanga mō te whakahaere ngātahi</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia whakatikaina ngā rara 46(3), 47(4), 48(4) hoki, kia mārama ai ia rōpū māna ake e pīkau ngā utu mō te whakaae ki ngā whakaaetanga mō te whakahaere ngātahi. Mā tēnei hoki ngā rara e ōrite ai ki ngā wāhanga i roto i te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato), ā, me te wete atu hoki i te kumukumu mā wai ngā utu e pīkau.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu hoki mātou, kia whakatikaina ngā rara 49(1), 49(2) mā te wete atu i te mea tonoa kia 10-rā te karanga mō te whakatū rōpū awheawhe ngātahi, i roto i ngā rā mahi e 10 atu i te rā mahi, i te whiwhinga rānei o te pānui a te Poari Kaitiaki Māori o Tūwharetoa, ā, me te whakakapi mā tētahi mea tonoa, kia whakatūria i roto wā rā mahi e 30. Kīhai te whakatū rōpū awheawhe ngātahi e tutuki i roto rā mahi e 10 engari, ka taea pai kēngia i roto wā rā mahi e 30, ā, ka ōrite hoki ki te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato).</text>
        </para>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Ngā Roto o Te Arawa</heading>
          <para>
            <text>I mea mai te Kaitiaki mō ngā Roto o Te Arawa ki a mātou, e toru ngā roto o Te Arawa i te rohenga wai o te Awa o Waikato ki Runga, ā, nō mai anō i tētahi whakataunga o te tau 2006 i tukua ai ki te kaitiaki, ā, kore rawa e whakakapia e ngā whakaritenga mō te whakahaere-tahi kei roto i te pire, ā, mā tēnei pea e kore ai te kaitiaki e kaha ki te uru atu ki ngā whakaritenga i te taha o ngā mana whakahaere ā-rohe, otirā, i te taha o Taiao Waikato.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Nō Te Arawa ngā kaiwhai pānga katoa o te kaitiaki, ā, nā reira, kei roto rātou i ngā whakaritenga mō te whakahaere-tahi a te Kaitiaki mō te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa. Ahakoa tā mātou kite atu i ngā āwangawanga o te Kaitiaki mō te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa, ki a mātou nei, me mahitahi rātou me te Kaitiaki mō te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa mō ngā whakaaetanga mō te whakahaere ngātahi kia kitea atu ai ngā pānga o Te Arawa, ā, me te āta titiro hoki kei te kapi ngā roto.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia kore he whakatikatika.</text>
          </para>
        </comm.lev2>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Te Awa o Waipā ki Runga</heading>
          <para>
            <text>Ahakoa i whakaaroarohia e mātou, kīhai tētahi tono a te Poari Kaitiaki Māori o Maniapoto i tautokona, kia whakatikaina te pire mā te whakauru whakamāramatanga mō te whakawhāiti i ngā pānga o Raukawa i te rohenga wai o te Awa o Waipā ki Runga, ā, me te hoatu wāhi mō Maniapoto kia uru atu ai ki ngā whakaaetanga mō te whakahaere ngātahi i waenganui i a Raukawa, me ngā mana whakahaere ā-rohe i roto iho i taua rohenga wai. He kaha tō mātou whakapono, mā te iwi ake ngā pānga inaki e whakatau, ehara mā te Karauna ki te tuhi ture mō ngā pānga iwi. Kei te whiriwhiri whakaaetanga a Māniapoto māna ake i te wā nei i te taha o te Karauna. Ngākau titikaha ana mātou, mā ēnei whiriwhiringa me te haere tonu o ngā kōrero i waenganui i a Raukawa me Maniapoto, e taea te kōkiri ngā māharahara o ngā iwi i whai wāhi ki roto. Ki a mātou nei, ka taea e te iwi te kōkiri ngā take e pā ana ki ngā pānga inaki i roto whakaritenga mō te whakahaere-tahi, kua hoatu i roto i te pire.</text>
          </para>
        </comm.lev2>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Ngāmema o te Mana Whakahaere o te Awa o Waikato</heading>
        <para>
          <text>I rongo mātou i ngā tāpaetanga e mea ana, kia nekehia atu ngā mema o te Mana Whakahaere o te Awa o Waikato, atu i te 10 ki te 12 kia whai māngai ai a Ngāti Korokī. Ko tērā i whakatakotoria, mā te Whetereihana o ngā Kaiahuwhenua o Aotearoa pea tētahi mema i tua atu e whakaingoa. Pērā anō i te wā i whakaaroarohia e mātou te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato), i whakaarotia nuitia e mātou te hiahia o Ngāti Korokī, kia arongia rātou hei iwi awa, ā, kia rongohia hoki ā rātou kōrero mō tō rātou Tupuna Awa. Ki tō mātou whakapono, me kimi huarahi mō rātou kia tutuki ai ō rātou tūmanako.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka noho tūturu tonu mātou, he pai ake te waiho i te rahi o ngā mema mō te Mana Whakahaere o te Awa o Waikato, ki te 10 kia tino oti pai ai ngā mahi. Kua kite hoki mātou, kei te āta tirohia anōtia ngā mema i te wā arotake o te mana whakahaere, ā tētahi rā kei te tū mai. Ki tō mātou mōhio i te wā nei, kei te whiriwhiri whakataunga te iwi mō ō rātou kerēme Tiriti hītori kore-raupatu i te taha o te Karauna. Ka whakahau mātou i a rāua tahi kia whakamahia te hātepe nei hei whai ake i ngā āwangawanga o te iwi.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia kore he whakatikatika.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Ngāture ārahi me ngā ture ā-rohe</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou, kia whakaurua he rara hou, ko rara 57(A) tērā, ki roto i te pire ki te whakamana i tētahi rara i roto i te whakaaetanga a Ngāti Tūwharetoa, kia pai ai te tiaki i ngā whakaritenga tū-i mua a te iwi.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>I rongo mātou i te māharahara o ngā māngai o te hunga hao ika arumoni, mō te pā kino o te pire ki ō rātou tika hao ika. Ko te whakamaherehere i whiwhi i a mātou, he rite te pire me te Ture Haonga Ika o te tau 1996, ā, kei ngā wāhanga i roto i te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato) ōna ritenga, ā, kore ana hoki e tuku mana ki te tāke i te hunga hao ika, ki te uta utu rānei ki runga i a rātou. E pēnei ana hoki te whakamaherehere ki a mātou, ko te tikanga, ka whakamahia te whakamātautau “undue adverse effects” e Te Tautiaki i ngā tini a Tangaroa, ki te whakatau mehemea me tuku ngā ture ā-rohe ki te kōtē, ki te aukati haonga ika rānei, kei te whakamahia wehekēngia i te wā nei, mō te haonga ika arumoni, mō te haonga ika tuku iho, tae atu hoki ki ngā momo haonga ika whakangahau, kia kore ai te tuwhena e pā kino i te haonga ika arumoni.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Kei te ngata mātou i te mea, ka haere tonu te rapu tohutohu i te hunga pupuri pānga i ngā wā ka hangaia he ture ārahi. Ki tā te pire, me hangaia i raro i te Ture Haonga Ika i te mea, kei reira tonu he wāhi i te wā nei mō te rapu tohutohu tika i te taha rōpū pāngia.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Te hononga ki te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato)</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Nā ngā whiriwhiringa i waenganui i te Karauna me Waikato-Tainui, i te whakataunga o ngā kerēme Tiriti e pā ana ki te Awa o Waikato, i whakatīmata te pou tarāwaho whakahaere tiaki kaupapa-tahi, me ngā whakaritenga ka pā ki te whakahaere-tahi mō te Awa o Waikato. Whai muri i tērā, ka haere tika a Ngāti Tūwharetoa, a Raukawa, me te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa ki te Karauna, ki te whiriwhiri whakaritenga mō rātou ake. Ka kitea anōtia ngā wāhanga whakaharahara o te pire nei, i roto i te Ture Whakataunga i ngā Kerēme Raupatu a Waikato-Tainui (mō te Awa o Waikato), ā, ki a mātou nei, he mea tika pea mō te pire ki te whakauru mihi mō te hononga i waenganui i ngā wāhi e rua o te hanganga ture. Mā tēnei hoki te mārama me te rite e whakatairanga, ā, e pai kē atu ai hoki tōna whakatinanatanga.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ahakoa tā mātou kore tūtohu whakatikatika i tēnei wā, ka whakatītina mātou i te Karauna kia matapaki i tēnei tūponotanga i te taha o ngā iwi katoa e whai wāhi ana, ā, me te whakatau whakatikatika hoki ki te hanganga ture i ngā rā tū mai.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.appendix>
        <heading>Tāpiritanga</heading>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Te hātepe o te komiti</heading>
          <para>
            <text>I tonoa te Pire a Ngati Tuwharetoa, Raukawa, me te Iwi Awa o Te Arawa mō te Awa o Waikato, ki te komiti i te 28 o Hōngongoi i te tau 2010. I kati ngā tāpaetanga i te 6 o Here-turi-kōkā i te tau 2010. E 18 ngā tāpaetanga i whiwhi, i whakaroarohia hoki mai i ngā rōpū whai pānga, ngā rōpū whakahaere ā-iwi, ngā mana whakahaere ā-rohe, ā, i te hunga pupuri pānga o te ao arumoni, o te ao ahuwhenua hoki. E 14 ngā tāpaetanga i rongohia e mātou i tētahi whakawātanga i Rotorua.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>I whiwhi whakamaherehere hoki mai i Te Tari Whakatau Take e pā ana ki te Tiriti o Waitangi.</text>
          </para>
        </comm.lev2>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Ngā mema o te komiti, ko</heading>
